You know what I think?  I think Anno got really mad at certain fans who criticized the way the TV series ended.  There was an outcry of displeasure among some anime fans at how the series ended and even a rumors that the series ending was the result of censorship.  The drastically different ending of the movie could have been the result of his contempt of those certain accusations and/or maybe because he &quot;had&quot; to redo the series ending through the movie's ending to &quot;please&quot; ALL the fans.  But he made it contradictory when compared to the tv series ending.<br>
